{"tid":1212174,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我發現好多廢佬話示威人士收左錢做野","createTime":"2019-06-12T17:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T10:19:08.000Z","uid":147219,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b5e5df8401b9da831064772507b8a1b48b9d7175","tid":1212174,"uid":147219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:35:36.000Z","msg":"不如大家整多啲圖廣傳，內容如下：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一班年輕人走到最前，<br />\n用自己既未來作為賭注，<br />\n冒著比人打、坐監、留案底、中槍既風險，都要走出黎。<br />\n仲有邊個覺得佢地收左錢？<br />\n比一萬蚊你，你肯？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或者<br />\n<br />\n6月9號收左錢？<br />\n一人一千蚊？<br />\n一百萬人十億？<br />\n十億啲人會得安全帽？<br />\n十億啲人會得口罩？<br />\n十億買到百幾架水炮車啦！<br />\n仲話啲人6月9收左錢？<br />\n<br />\n小弟不才，諗唔到好既句子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家要努力，天佑香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d17eda43b6309c6f498ec433b39fe22fb45b4b","tid":1212174,"uid":147219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:36:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7b408c29e92a3f229c5a57a5b176af0580f1ff3d","tid":1212174,"uid":147219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:36:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4bfc6d811d5c808827a91393c165706b39e88231","tid":1212174,"uid":12197,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:38:45.000Z","msg":"今日睇到都嬲 有外國勢力 有資金support 洗淨係得d 外科口罩 ? 輪到我地重裝了"},{"pid":"37529f634cb154d936ac67d24bc5c6560d758d11","tid":1212174,"uid":75041,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:39:08.000Z","msg":"同班零生產力既垃圾講<br />\n<br />\n「係呀，係幾好搵架，不過我都搵夠啦，係哩，有無興趣一齊賺下錢呀屌你老母臭閪？」"},{"pid":"86c7092f8a652ee6fbca2b38f346c4a17f7aa47b","tid":1212174,"uid":190521,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:39:14.000Z","msg":"因為好多藍絲同樣係收左錢做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以己度人，咪用返呢套邏輯話你地"},{"pid":"3bb0d787e6accfc64171c7e4386b63ab